---
// Dress code section
---

<section id="dresscode" class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-water-light mb-2">Código de Vestimenta</h2>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-silver"></span>
      <span class="text-water-light text-sm">✧</span>
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-silver"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="inline-block px-8 py-6 rounded-2xl bg-water-deep/40 border border-water-mid/20">
      <p class="text-2xl text-water-light font-semibold mb-3">Formal / Elegante</p>
      <p class="text-water-mid/70 text-sm max-w-md">
        Te pedimos vestir de manera formal para esta ocasión tan especial.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Color palette -->
    <div class="mt-10">
      <p class="text-water-mid/50 font-[Montserrat] text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Paleta sugerida</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#1a3a5c] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Azul profundo"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#7ec8e3] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Azul cielo"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#c0c0c0] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Plata"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#9b8ec4] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Lavanda"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#e8e8e8] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Blanco perla"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- No white notice -->
    <p class="mt-6 text-water-mid/40 text-sm italic">
      ✧ Se solicita amablemente no vestir de blanco ni azul cielo ✧
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
